title: Lena Dunham is Caroline Calloway's Kind of Girl
description: Buckle up for an episode we've been dreaming of for our entire lives. After our coverage of Lena Dunham last week, one Caroline Calloway reached out to let us know we hadn't done the book justice. Internet phenom, instagram sensation, and scam queen Caroline offers the context we overlooked in our first round of Dunham talk for this discussion slash occasional heated debate. Follow Caroline on Tik Tok!!!!https://www.tiktok.com/@carolinecalloway?lang=enAnd on Instagramhttps://www.instagram.com/carolinecalloway/?hl=enTees are Here!! Grab a Worm Tee or an Unhinged Tee: https://celebritymemoirbookclub.square.site/Follow us on Twitter @cmbc_podcast and Instagram @celebritymemoirbookclub If you want even more juice subscribe to our patreon!!! This week we’re talking about Carol Dunham's art with a professional artist!!! (@katherineparkerart)And don't miss last week's Patreon episode with our most unfiltered Dunham thoughtshttps://www.patreon.com/celebritymemoirbookclub Art by @adrianne_manpearl and theme song by @ashleesimpsonrossSupport the show
